survey_response.review_text: Great treatment by doctor. He was very friendly and polite with patient. He analyses the root cause very wel and starts the treatment with medication instead of directly jumping to the conclusion of surgery.

Most of the communication was on WhatsApp which saved me a lot of time. I already started recommending the doctor for few of my friends. I am happy with my ACL reconstruction.

survey_response.review_text: On January 8th 2022,I had left knee injury.After diagnosis it resulted in ACL tear and I was recommended to Hosmat hospital.My wife has did lot of research about doctors and decided to consult Dr.Harish G Puranik sir.Believe my words he is such a expert and friendly ,kind..he is more than his  reviews .prior to consulting him others doctors prescribed immediate  surgery .But After consulting him he told me to recover from internal injury and go for surgery.On February 11th 2022 he did my surgery.Surgery went for 1 hr 30 mins where he did ACL reconstruction and partial meniscus repair.I still remember during surgery time he is so cool and showed me what happened and how he is repairing it ,Believe me he was humming songs during that time .Overall surgery went successful and I have started my recovery process.

Explanation of the problem.

For any updation of refer by doctor... They didn't ask about anything. Themselves filled the format.

doctor will answer the queries of patients with good explanation , caring for patients,and if any clarification required for patients that will be given by phone/whats up . Highly recommended doctor for those who are need of good treatment and care.
Thank you very much sir for giving me good treatment
